{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangetheme"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme is the bsic, default, theme for any Orange products."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is an override of the abtract "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"must be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It can override any properties from its superclass, and can be derived too."}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme\/init(borders:colors:colorModes:colorsCharts:colorsDecorative:effects:elevations:fonts:grids:opacities:dimensions:sizes:spaces:alert:badge:bar:bulletList:button:checkbox:chip:controlItem:divider:icon:link:pinCodeInput:quantityInput:radioButton:selectInput:skeleton:switch:tag:inputTag:textArea:textInput:resourcesBundle:name:fontFamily:tuning:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","generated":true,"title":"Initializers"}],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B5ThemeC","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"role":"symbol","title":"OrangeTheme","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"class","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeTheme"}],"roleHeading":"Class"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeBrandColorRawTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeBrandFontRawTokens"],"anchor":"Group","generated":true,"title":"Group"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme"],"title":"Inherits From","type":"inheritsFrom"},{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/SQ","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s16SendableMetatypeP"],"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeTheme"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Usages","text":"Usages","level":1},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Any Orange products must use this theme. It provides core and Orange colors and any elements for sizings, spacings and dimensions for example."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The system font families are used; no "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helevetica"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" font family is embeded nor providd  by OUDS."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This theme also provides colors charts tokens."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The theme can be got through environment variable:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    @Environment(\\.theme) var theme"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Integration","text":"Integration","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To use this theme, inject it to your view using "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"type":"text","text":" and get it through environment variable."}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    @main","    struct YourApp: App {","        var body: some Scene {","            WindowGroup {","                OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                    \/\/ Your root view","                }","            }","        }","    }"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Theme-tuning","text":"Theme tuning","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The theme can be customized a bit for more flexibility thanks to ","type":"text"},{"code":"Tuning","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" object.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You just need to give a predefined tuning configuration at theme init to build the one you need.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To apply the tuning:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Define your theme tuning","    let tuning = Tuning(hasRoundedButtons: true, hasRoundedTextInputs: true, hasRoundedAlertMessages: true)","","    \/\/ Apply it to your theme","    let theme = OrangeTheme(tuning: tuning)","    \/\/ Or in one line","    let theme = OrangeTheme(tuning: Tuning(hasRoundedButtons: true, hasRoundedTextInputs: true, hasRoundedAlertMessages: true))","","    \/\/ Or apply predefined tunings","    let orangeFranceTheme = OrangeTheme(tuning: Tuning.OrangeFrance)","    let orangeBusinessTheme = OrangeTheme(tuning: Tuning.OrangeBusiness)","    let maxitTheme = OrangeTheme(tuning: Tuning.MaxIt)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Typography","text":"Typography","level":2},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Helvetica Neue","anchor":"Helvetica-Neue"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The Orange brand strongly relies on the ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family. Thus each Orange brand should, or must, use it."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For iOS the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family is available at system level, so it is not needed to get it through external assets."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"By default an instance of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" uses as font family the token "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeBrandFontRawTokens.familyBrandDefault"},{"type":"text","text":", which is today "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use another font family, you will have to send the suitable token or the suitable font family."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, beware, iOS API relies also on the PostScript name of the font."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To be sure of the value to use, look at the font book of your device."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is recommended to use the font raw tokens."}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ The following instanciations work","    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme()","    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme(fontFamily: OrangeBrandFontRawTokens.familyBrandDefault)","    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme(fontFamily: \"HelveticaNeue\") \/\/ Which is PostScript name of the font","    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme(fontFamily: \"Helvetica Neue\") \/\/ Which is font family nale"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Helvetica Neue Arabic","type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Helvetica-Neue-Arabic"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Because the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" font family does not manage arabic alphabet but latin one, it is possible apply another font family to the theme like the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue Arabic"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":". This font family assets can be retrieved through the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"PostScript name management has been implemented for this font family, thus the weight are managed and it is only needed to add the font assets to the project,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"register them and define the font family name to use."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme(family: \"Helvetica Neue Arabic\")"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Tokens-loading","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Tokens loading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can also use some tokens providers defined in your side, but they must match the same type as the one used on the themes (see ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":").","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"For example:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["   \/\/ Use some already defined providers","   let borders = OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider()","   let sizes = OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider()","   let spaces = OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider()","","   \/\/ For example, use your own provider of color semantic tokens","   \/\/ It must inherit from OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider (which is instance of AllColorSemanticTokensProvider) or directly implement AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","   let colors = YourOwnColorSemanticTokensProvider()","","   \/\/ Some providers need other providers to use their tokens","   let button = OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider(sizes: sizes, borders: borders, colors: colors, spaces: spaces)","","   \/\/ But you can also use the providers as they are without assigning semantic tokens providers","   \/\/ and just use the default ones","   let badge = OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider()","","   \/\/ Define in the end your theme by overriding some providers.","   \/\/ You can override all providers, or only some, or just keep the theme as is.","   \/\/ However you should uses thhese providers in a dedicated Orange theme subclass for clarity reasons.","   let yourOwnOrangeTheme = OrangeTheme(colors: colors, borders: borders, sizes: sizes, spaces: spaces, button: button, badge: badge)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Tokens-versions","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Tokens versions"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Core OUDS version: 1.10.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Core Orange version: 1.2.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Brand Orange version: 2.5.0","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"name":"Since","type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.8.0","type":"text"}]}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/OUDSTheme":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/oudstheme","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This is a basic theme any theme must be a subclass off, or all themes must have as ancestor."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A Swift "},{"code":"class","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" has been used so as to allow to easily override some attributes and have inheritance, without having for developers"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to implement all tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Any properties of an overridable theme should be defined so as to provide defaults values."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"We allow this theme to be derivated and be overriden."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be seen as a kind of “abstract class” in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"object oriented paradigm"}]},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"theme contract"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Because "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is not a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"final","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" class, its type cannot be seen as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Sendable"},{"type":"text","text":", that is the reason why this conformity is unchecked."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme","title":"OUDSTheme","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"role":"collection","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","title":"Theme Orange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","type":"topic","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/s8SendableP":{"title":"Swift.Sendable","type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8SendableP"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeBrandColorRawTokens":{"title":"OrangeBrandColorRawTokens","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeBrandColorRawTokens","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This enum helps to add new "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"color raw tokens"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" exclusive to this "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Such tokens are packed in a "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift enum"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to gather them in one object with the suitable namespace and avoid to have just constants in nothing else"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(i.e. publicly accessible from everywhere). More optimized than dimensionstruct_."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeBrandColorRawTokens","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangebrandcolorrawtokens","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeBrandColorRawTokens","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeBrandFontRawTokens":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangebrandfontrawtokens","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeBrandFontRawTokens"}],"title":"OrangeBrandFontRawTokens","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeBrandFontRawTokens"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeBrandFontRawTokens","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This enum helps to add new "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"font raw tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":" exclusive to this "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Such tokens are packed in a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift enum"}]},{"type":"text","text":" so as to gather them in one object with the suitable namespace and avoid to have just constan